{"tid":661209,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(HR巴絲入) 合約最後一日一定要返工？","createTime":"2018-05-11T10:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T11:02:48.000Z","uid":103530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf9cf8477f187afbb7446fbee3a7f762cac14e7","tid":661209,"uid":103530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:56:54.000Z","msg":"份約就完，臨完約前公司安排左放大假，放到完約前最後一日。因為老板話勞工法例規定左合約最後一日一定要返工，唔係出唔到糧。而我係又衰仔既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，買機票果陣無留意到返唔切黎返最後一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n我搵過類似問題，只係搵到離職日只需要係通知日起計一個月後既前一日，不論係咪上班日。但無資料話完約最後一日係咪一定要返，同埋其實我會續約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。所以想問勞工法例其實有無話合約期最後一日一定要返工？麻煩各位HR巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/183313_fd5687aef0453ae3c8e80891f8b288f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F183313_fd5687aef0453ae3c8e80891f8b288f6.png&h=02f8ceea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：如果勞工法例無問題，其實老板俾會請假"},{"pid":"57ecdddfb822238fb3f2148f9a01b1539c6075fd","tid":661209,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"你同佢講7日唔出糧勞工處見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaf114aabe8c2ba7e0d32056aa4138d747431c0","tid":661209,"uid":115082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"7日唔出糧 Bye"}]}